name: Dreams Inside Rooms Dreams Inside Scapes

metadata.name: Trees Grow out of this Window
metadata.description:
Experimentations with AI, Glitch, VR and Blender.  

Homemade Blender scapes are fed into DALL E 2 and the characters are created with Stable Diffusion. Collaged in a photo editor, taken into Blender to add 3d assets hand sculpted in Virtual Reality. Rendered and then pixel sorted. 

Using an array of tools to portray my dreams, moods, and fantasies.
